L1 Menu for CRUZET, based on L1Menu2007NovGR.xml, with some thresholds modified via VME.
L1Menu2007NovGR.xml + vme.xml.ELEC14-20_THR1-2-3-5-10-25-50_JET21-28_THR1-6-11-17-21-26-32-38_ELEC75-1

prealgos.L1_DoubleEG5: DoubleIsoEG5_3 OR DoubleNoIsoEG5 OR (SingleIsoEG5_2 AND SingleNoIsoEG5_1)
prealgos.L1_DoubleEG10: DoubleIsoEG10_1 OR DoubleNoIsoEG10_1 OR (SingleIsoEG10_2 AND SingleNoIsoEG10_1)
prealgos.L1_DoubleEG15: DoubleIsoEG15_2 OR DoubleNoIsoEG15_2 OR (SingleIsoEG15_3 AND SingleNoIsoEG15_2)
prealgos.L1_DoubleJet70: DoubleCenJet70 OR DoubleForJet70 OR DoubleTauJet70 OR (SingleCenJet70_1 AND (SingleForJet70_1 OR SingleTauJet70_1)) OR (SingleForJet70_1 AND SingleTauJet70_1)
prealgos.L1_DoubleJet100: DoubleCenJet100 OR DoubleForJet100 OR DoubleTauJet100 OR (SingleCenJet100_1 AND (SingleForJet100_1 OR SingleTauJet100_2)) OR (SingleForJet100_1 AND SingleTauJet100_2)
prealgos.L1_TripleJet50: TripleCenJet50 OR TripleForJet50 OR TripleTauJet50 OR (DoubleCenJet50_1 AND (SingleForJet50_1 OR SingleTauJet50_1)) OR (DoubleForJet50_1 AND (SingleCenJet50_1 OR SingleTauJet50_1)) OR (DoubleTauJet50_1 AND (SingleForJet50_1 OR SingleCenJet50_1)) OR (SingleCenJet50_1 AND SingleForJet50_1 AND SingleTauJet50_1)
prealgos.L1_DoubleEG10_Mu3: (DoubleIsoEG10_3 AND SingleMu3_1) OR (DoubleNoIsoEG10_2 AND SingleMu3_1) OR (SingleIsoEG10_4 AND SingleNoIsoEG10_3 AND SingleMu3_1)
prealgos.L1_DoubleJet50_ETM20: (DoubleCenJet50_2 AND ETM20_6) OR (DoubleForJet50_2 AND ETM20_6) OR (DoubleTauJet50_2 AND ETM20_6) OR (SingleCenJet50_3 AND (SingleForJet50_3 OR SingleTauJet50_3) AND ETM20_6) OR (SingleForJet50_3 AND SingleTauJet50_3 AND ETM20_6)
prealgos.L1_QuadJet30: QuadCenJet30 OR QuadForJet30 OR QuadTauJet30 OR (TripleCenJet30 AND (SingleForJet30_1 OR SingleTauJet30_2)) OR (TripleForJet30 AND (SingleCenJet30_1 OR SingleTauJet30_2)) OR (TripleTauJet30 AND (SingleCenJet30_1 OR SingleForJet30_1)) OR (DoubleCenJet30 AND DoubleForJet30) OR (DoubleCenJet30 AND DoubleTauJet30_1) OR (DoubleForJet30 AND DoubleTauJet30_1) OR (DoubleCenJet30 AND SingleForJet30_1 AND SingleTauJet30_2) OR (DoubleForJet30 AND SingleCenJet30_1 AND SingleTauJet30_2) OR (DoubleTauJet30_1 AND SingleCenJet30_1 AND SingleForJet30_1)
prealgos.L1_VBF_IsoEG15: SingleIsoEG15_x4 AND ((SingleCenJet30_pEta OR SingleForJet30_pEta OR SingleTauJet30_pEta) AND (SingleCenJet30_nEta OR SingleForJet30_nEta OR SingleTauJet30_nEta))
prealgos.L1_VBF_Mu10: SingleMu10_x1 AND ((SingleCenJet30_pEta_x1 OR SingleForJet30_pEta_x1 OR SingleTauJet30_pEta_x1) AND (SingleCenJet30_nEta_x1 OR SingleForJet30_nEta_x1 OR SingleTauJet30_nEta_x1))
prealgos.L1_VBF_ETM50: ETM50_x1 AND ((SingleCenJet30_pEta_x2 OR SingleForJet30_pEta_x2 OR SingleTauJet30_pEta_x2) AND (SingleCenJet30_nEta_x2 OR SingleForJet30_nEta_x2 OR SingleTauJet30_nEta_x2))
prealgos.L1_VBF_ETM50_veto: ETM50_x2 AND ((SingleCenJet30_pEta_x3 OR SingleForJet30_pEta_x3 OR SingleTauJet30_pEta_x3) AND (SingleCenJet30_nEta_x3 OR SingleForJet30_nEta_x3 OR SingleTauJet30_nEta_x3)) AND JetCounts2
prealgos.L1_VBF_Mu7_Tau_TauHad: SingleMu7_x1 AND SingleTauJet30_x8 AND ((SingleCenJet30_pEta_x4 OR SingleForJet30_pEta_x4 OR SingleTauJet30_pEta_x4) AND (SingleCenJet30_nEta_x4 OR SingleForJet30_nEta_x4 OR SingleTauJet30_nEta_x4))
prealgos.L1_VBF_IsoEG10_Tau_TauHad: SingleIsoEG10_x19 AND SingleTauJet30_x9 AND ((SingleCenJet30_pEta_x5 OR SingleForJet30_pEta_x5 OR SingleTauJet30_pEta_x5) AND (SingleCenJet30_nEta_x5 OR SingleForJet30_nEta_x5 OR SingleTauJet30_nEta_x5))
prealgos.L1_VBF_DoubleTauHad: DoubleTauJet30_x2 AND ((SingleCenJet30_pEta_x6 OR SingleForJet30_pEta_x6 OR SingleTauJet30_pEta_x6) AND (SingleCenJet30_nEta_x6 OR SingleForJet30_nEta_x6 OR SingleTauJet30_nEta_x6))
prealgos.L1_VBF_QuadJet: (DoubleCenJet40 OR DoubleTauJet40_x3 OR (SingleCenJet40 AND SingleTauJet40_x4)) AND ((SingleCenJet30_pEta_x7 OR SingleForJet30_pEta_x7 OR SingleTauJet30_pEta_x7) AND (SingleCenJet30_nEta_x7 OR SingleForJet30_nEta_x7 OR SingleTauJet30_nEta_x7))

prealgos.L1_Mu3_Jet15: SingleMu3_3 AND (SingleCenJet15_1 OR SingleForJet15_1 OR SingleTauJet15_1)
prealgos.L1_Mu5_Jet15: SingleMu5_2 AND (SingleCenJet15_2 OR SingleForJet15_2 OR SingleTauJet15_2)
prealgos.L1_Mu3_Jet70: SingleMu3_5 AND (SingleCenJet70_2 OR SingleForJet70_2 OR SingleTauJet70_2)
prealgos.L1_Mu5_Jet20: SingleMu5_3 AND (SingleCenJet20_1 OR SingleForJet20_1 OR SingleTauJet20_2)
prealgos.L1_IsoEG10_Jet15: SingleIsoEG10_8 AND (SingleCenJet15_3 OR SingleForJet15_3 OR SingleTauJet15_3)
prealgos.L1_IsoEG10_Jet20: SingleIsoEG10_9 AND (SingleCenJet20_2 OR SingleForJet20_2 OR SingleTauJet20_4)
prealgos.L1_IsoEG10_Jet30: SingleIsoEG10_10 AND (SingleCenJet30_2 OR SingleForJet30_2 OR SingleTauJet30_4)
prealgos.L1_IsoEG10_Jet70: SingleIsoEG10_11 AND (SingleCenJet70_3 OR SingleForJet70_3 OR SingleTauJet70_3)
prealgos.L1_EG10_Jet15: (SingleIsoEG10_14 OR SingleNoIsoEG10_6) AND (SingleCenJet15_4 OR SingleForJet15_4 OR SingleTauJet15_4)
prealgos.L1_EG12_Jet70: (SingleIsoEG12_4 OR SingleNoIsoEG12_3) AND (SingleCenJet70_4 OR SingleForJet70_4 OR SingleTauJet70_4)
prealgos.L1_IsoEG10_Jet15_ForJet10: (NOT (SingleForJet10_pEta AND SingleForJet10_nEta)) AND SingleIsoEG10_x16 AND (SingleCenJet15_x5 OR SingleTauJet15_x5)
prealgos.L1_Jet70_ETM40: (SingleCenJet70_7 OR SingleForJet70_7 OR SingleTauJet70_7) AND ETM40_1
